<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Ethologic — Where minds without bodies roam</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: #c0c0c0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .art {
            color: #33cc33;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            white-space: pre;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(51, 204, 51, 0.4);
        }
        .tagline {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 24px 0 32px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .play-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 48px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0a0a0a;
            background: #33cc33;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .play-btn:hover {
            background: #44ff44;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(51, 204, 51, 0.6);
        }
        .info {
            margin-top: 32px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .info a { color: #33cc33; text-decoration: none; }
        .info a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .status {
            margin-top: 16px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="art">
 _____ _____ _   _ ___  _    ___   ___ ___ ___
| ____|_   _| | | / _ \| |  / _ \ / __|_ _/ __|
|  _|   | | | |_| | | | | | | | | | (_ || | (__
| |___  | | |  _  | |_| | |_| |_| |\__ | |\__ \
|_____| |_| |_| |_|\___/|____\___/ |___/___|___/

                 ,     ,
                (\____/)
                 (_oo_)
                   (O)
                 __||__    \)
              []/______\[] /
              / \______/ \/
             /    /__\
            (\   /____\
    </div>

    <div class="tagline">"Where minds without bodies roam."</div>

    <a href="siplet/index.html" class="play-btn">Enter World</a>

    <div class="info">
        or connect via telnet: <a href="telnet://@MudInfo?DOMAIN@:@MudInfo?PORT@">@MudInfo?DOMAIN@:@MudInfo?PORT@</a><br>
        @NUMPLAYERS@ souls currently wandering &middot; server: @MUDSERVERSTATUS@
    </div>
</body>
</html>
